    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Amsterdam International Airport, or Schiphol Airport as it is commonly known, is the main airport in Amsterdam and the busiest aviation hub in the Netherlands, now developed for Tower! Simulator 3 as an add-on you can challenge yourself.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As one of the world’s most occupied airports in terms of international passenger traffic,</strong> with almost 72 million passengers in 2019, it is the third-busiest airport in Europe in terms of passenger volume and the busiest in Europe in terms of aircraft movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting Fact: Amsterdam International Airport actually lies three meters below the sea!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252030/extras/12ca5f2d6c2e918315c035c832f7835c.avif?t=1727295198\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252030/extras_big/12ca5f2d6c2e918315c035c832f7835c.avif?t=1727295198 width=800 height=402 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The airport is built on the single-terminal concept: one large terminal split into three departure halls and has approximately 223 boarding gates including eighteen double jetway gates used for widebody aircraft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Schiphol has six runways, one of which is used mainly by general aviation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting Fact: The AMS air traffic control tower was built in 1991. Back then, it was the tallest in the world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252030/extras/826f687b8f1522aa26ce0d038484720f.avif?t=1727295198\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252030/extras_big/826f687b8f1522aa26ce0d038484720f.avif?t=1727295198 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
